<h1>The MIDI Manager</h1>

<p>The MIDI Manager is a singleton object that keeps track of the state of
the MIDI system and any connected MIDI devices.  It provides 
methods for querying that state as well as assorted utility methods.</p>

<p>The shared MIDI Manager instance can be returned by calling:</p>

<blockquote>
<pre>
	PYMIDIManager* manager = [PYMIDIManager sharedInstance];
</pre>
</blockquote>

